Note:
When you create an Ingress in Google Kubernetes Engine, Kubernetes automatically creates a Google Cloud HTTP(S) Load Balancer.
The external LB needs a way to reach your pods. But with ClusterIP, the lb cannot directly reach the pods.

Option 1: Internet --> Google Load Balancer --> NodePort --> NodePort  ---> Worker Node  --> Pods
Option 2: Interent --> Google Load Balancer --> NEG(Network Endpoint Group) --> Pods directly. LB connects directly yo pods.
